<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA35">
<l>kāṇkā ṇeṉavirumpuṅ kaṇkaḷ katirilaku</l>
<l>pūṇṭā rakalattāṉ poṉmēṉi – pāṇkaṭ</l>
<l>ṭoḻilpāṭi vaṇṭaṟaiyun toṅkalāṉ cempoṟ</l>
<l>kaḻalpāṭi yāntoḻutum kai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘Look, look,’ thus desire the eyes: the golden body of him</l>
<l>whose chest has ornaments shining with rays [and] garlands.</l>
<l>The red-golden anklet of him with the pendant, around which bees hum,</l>
<l>busily singing melodies, we will sing [and] worship, hands [folded].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
